fr.univrennes1.cri.jtacl.core.network
Class Iface

java.lang.Object
  fr.univrennes1.cri.jtacl.core.network.Iface

public class Iface
extends java.lang.Object

Describes a network interface.

An interface is part of a NetworkEquipment network equipment, has some IfaceLink links to the network and a name.
Probes Probe are received from the network via the incoming() method and sent via the outgoing() method.

Author:
Patrick Lamaiziere
